      "end": 570.27,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.27,
      "end": 571.67,
      "text": "That's what an auction"
    },
    {
      "start": 571.67,
      "end": 572.83,
      "text": "is all about"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.83,
      "end": 573.91,
      "text": "Hey, $5"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.91,
      "end": 574.59,
      "text": "Oh, $10"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.59,
      "end": 575.15,
      "text": "$20"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.15,
      "end": 576.51,
      "text": "It keeps going up"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.51,
      "end": 577.11,
      "text": "Yeah, right"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.11,
      "end": 579.03,
      "text": "Until the highest bidder"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.03,
      "end": 580.87,
      "text": "gets the price"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.87,
      "end": 581.25,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.25,
      "end": 582.65,
      "text": "They get to buy the item"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.65,
      "end": 583.17,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 583.17,
      "end": 584.53,
      "text": "So there's someone"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.53,
      "end": 585.69,
      "text": "who has more power"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.69,
      "end": 586.67,
      "text": "over them, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 587.13,
      "end": 588.15,
      "text": "이 Morgan 같은 사람"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.15,
      "end": 589.05,
      "text": "더 큰 손이"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.05,
      "end": 590.29,
      "text": "이렇게 위에 있다라는 것을"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.29,
      "end": 591.11,
      "text": "좀 알게 해준"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.11,
      "end": 592.03,
      "text": "장면이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.03,
      "end": 593.77,
      "text": "자, 이 내용 떠올리시면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.77,
      "end": 594.73,
      "text": "한번 더 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 594.73,
      "end": 596.11,
      "text": "It's a shame"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.11,
      "end": 597.31,
      "text": "But I'm here to help"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.31,
      "end": 598.51,
      "text": "Now I know that you"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.51,
      "end": 599.83,
      "text": "you wish Edison"
    },
    {
      "start": 599.83,
      "end": 600.53,
      "text": "a quiet down"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.53,
      "end": 601.67,
      "text": "So let me"
    },
    {
      "start": 601.67,
      "end": 603.15,
      "text": "combine your companies"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.15,
      "end": 603.81,
      "text": "Let me clean up"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.81,
      "end": 604.15,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.15,
      "end": 606.29,
      "text": "You really think"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.29,
      "end": 607.45,
      "text": "Westinghouse Electric"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.45,
      "end": 608.53,
      "text": "is worth $5 million"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.53,
      "end": 610.31,
      "text": "The value of something"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.31,
      "end": 611.17,
      "text": "is the highest number"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.17,
      "end": 611.75,
      "text": "someone else"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.75,
      "end": 612.65,
      "text": "is wanting to pay"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.65,
      "end": 615.65,
      "text": "Wow, 다음 전개가"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.65,
      "end": 616.69,
      "text": "어떻게 될지"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.69,
      "end": 618.65,
      "text": "합병이 과연 될지"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.65,
      "end": 620.89,
      "text": "에디슨은 어떻게 반응을 할지"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.89,
      "end": 622.49,
      "text": "너무 흥미진진합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.49,
      "end": 623.97,
      "text": "Things are getting interesting"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.97,
      "end": 624.35,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.35,
      "end": 625.23,
      "text": "Very interesting"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.23,
      "end": 626.59,
      "text": "Yeah, 기대해 주시고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.59,
      "end": 629.33,
      "text": "오늘 여기에서 또 마무리해 보도록 하겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.33,
      "end": 630.23,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.23,
      "end": 631.43,
      "text": "마무리하시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.43,
      "end": 634.79,
      "text": "자, 다음 주 월요일에 만날게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 634.79,
      "end": 635.27,
      "text": "크리스"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.27,
      "end": 636.09,
      "text": "I'll see you Monday"
    }
  ]
}